OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784315922
OL,3,CEx-DUP leader Jeffrey Donaldson will
OL,4,Cappeal rape and sexual assault
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson has lodged an appeal
OL,8,Fof his conviction for child sexual
OL,9,Fabuse and rape.
OL,11,FThe former DUP leader and MP's legal
OL,12,Fteam confirmed they had started the
OL,13,Fprocess as the deadline loomed.
OL,15,FHis solicitor John McBurney said: "I
OL,16,Fcan confirm having lodged on behalf of
OL,17,FJeffrey Donaldson appeal papers with
OL,18,Fthe relevant office at the Court of
OL,19,FAppeal."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
