CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784315922
OL,3,CEx-DUP leader Jeffrey Donaldson will
OL,4,Cappeal rape and sexual assault
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FUTV understands leave to appeal will
OL,8,Fbe decided in September and if it is
OL,9,Fgranted an appeal hearing could come
OL,10,Fas early as October. If he is
OL,11,Fsuccessful in the appeal there would
OL,12,Fbe a retrial.
OL,14,FDonaldson is currently in Maghaberry
OL,15,FPrison as he awaits sentencing after
OL,16,Fhe was convicted of 18 counts of
OL,17,Fsexual abuse against two women when
OL,18,Fthey were children.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
