OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784315922
OL,3,CEx-DUP leader Jeffrey Donaldson will
OL,4,Cappeal rape and sexual assault
OL,5,Cconviction
OL,7,FHis wife, Eleanor Donaldson, faced a
OL,8,Ftrial of the facts and it found she
OL,9,Fhad aided and abetted her abuser
OL,10,Fhusband. The case ran for four weeks
OL,11,Funtil the jury reached their verdicts
OL,12,Fon June 22.
